title: Joe Jackson - Live (2012 AXS.TV) [FLAC, Audio Only]
description:
Recorded from live broadcast on AXS.TV.
Performance at Count Basie Theatre in Red Bank, NJ, September 25, 2012, with special guest Regina Carter on violin.
Tour in support of Joe Jackson's album "The Duke".
Concert includes Duke Ellington standards and Joe's own hits.
Minor editing to remove several minutes worth of chit chat between songs. (Some chit chat left intact for effect.)

Motorola DVR analog outputs to Creative SoundBlaster X-Fi HD. A few minor glitches in audio were present in the original broadcast.
